Dialogue: 5,0:00:15.05,0:00:17.28,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,Mu, I really think...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:17.79,0:00:21.07,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I really think I want to become an astronaut.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.91,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,I believe I can make it to the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:23.87,0:00:25.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}H-He beat me to it!
Dialogue: 5,0:00:26.02,0:00:27.21,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,What about you, Mu?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:29.21,0:00:33.84,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,If you're going to the moon, then I'll stay one step ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:37.71,0:00:38.71,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'm...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:40.85,0:00:42.41,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,going to Mars.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.19,0:00:52.20,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}A big brother should always stay ahead of his little brother.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:54.49,0:00:58.99,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}That is what I have always believed.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:01.76,0:01:04.91,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}But Hibito was always the one moving ahead...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.88,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Leaving me behind.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:15.32,0:01:19.88,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Have I finally caught up, Hibito?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:21.17,0:01:25.36,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or are you still...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:25.98,0:01:25.98,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:43.04,OP,,0,0,0,,I can't get lost in what I'm doing, nothing works out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.04,0:01:45.58,OP,,0,0,0,,I don't want these endlessly dull days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:47.83,OP,,0,0,0,,I hope I can move on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:49.50,OP,,0,0,0,,before the call of freedom drags me away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:01:51.67,OP,,0,0,0,,What's your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:53.46,OP,,0,0,0,,I just want some real courage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:56.34,OP,,0,0,0,,We all stare doubt in the face, every one of us
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:02:00.26,OP,,0,0,0,,Isn't the unpredictability of life the fun of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:04.02,OP,,0,0,0,,Devote your life to that dream you can't express
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:07.89,OP,,0,0,0,,Let's go, advance against the wind, our road is long
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:11.90,OP,,0,0,0,,Embrace the pain of it too
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:15.86,OP,,0,0,0,,Take a big breath now, and yell
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:23.74,OP,,0,0,0,,Big Bang! Chase it without fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.74,0:02:33.46,OP,,0,0,0,,I want to dream so badly it amazes me
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:42.93,OP,,0,0,0,,There's cowardice in the way of your true wish
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.93,0:02:48.98,OP,,0,0,0,,Rip that thick veil aside
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.03,0:02:56.03,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.00,0:03:01.23,Default,A,0,0,0,,This simulation's purpose was to perform the next step.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:02.08,0:03:05.88,Default,A,0,0,0,,I believe that the CAPCOM schedule indicated that setting B
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.28,0:03:08.20,title,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\fad(444,638)\fax-0.15\bord0\blur0.5\c&HEFEAED&\4c&H000000&\pos(946,8)}#99 Life Changes, Promises Don't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:08.20,title,EpTitle,0,0,0,,{\fad(444,638)\fax-0.15\1a&HFF&\blur1.5\bord1\3c&H1C2E3A&\pos(946,8)}#99 Life Changes, Promises Don't
Dialogue: 5,0:03:06.64,0:03:10.59,Default,A,0,0,0,,would be used on approach to the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:10.59,0:03:11.46,Default,A,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.28,0:03:18.52,Default,A,0,0,0,,In my absence, CAPCOM gave the go ahead to use setting A.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.52,0:03:22.33,Default,A,0,0,0,,That's the reason this landing ended in failure.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:31.98,0:03:33.49,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, Mutta.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.17,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,{\i1}I noticed your mistake...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:36.98,0:03:40.11,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,{\i1}But during this training, your performance is under review.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.03,0:03:45.11,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know why you're having trouble concentrating.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.84,0:03:46.67,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.05,0:03:50.75,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was hoping you would notice your mistake,
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.57,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,{\i1}despite everything else that's happening.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.39,0:04:04.86,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Why did you give us the go ahead before you checked with the flight director?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:04.86,0:04:09.41,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,CAPCOM's role is to communicate with the crew.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:09.41,0:04:12.14,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,You do not have the authority to make decisions.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:13.22,0:04:17.11,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Yes, it was poor judgment on my part.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:17.11,0:04:20.49,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,It's baffling that such a rudimentary mistake could even happen.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.16,0:04:23.91,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,This may be a simulation, but that doesn't mean you can be careless.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.70,0:04:29.24,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Act like you're on missions during training, and act like you're training during missions.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.12,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,That is the attitude we must adopt.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.34,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,During this simulation, what were you thinking?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.51,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.17,0:04:45.01,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I believe my mind wasn't on the task at hand.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.44,0:04:49.73,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,As I've said many times, we must be on the same wavelength.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.73,0:04:56.62,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,I hope you realize that if you continue to underperform, you will be considered unqualified as my backup.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.65,0:05:02.69,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:03.38,0:05:05.66,Default,A,0,0,0,,Then that's all for this meeting.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.30,0:05:25.22,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,I snorted when I heard you tell him to be on your wavelength... Like it's even possible.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.33,0:05:32.53,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,This will be my first time on the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:33.34,0:05:37.77,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,I want to ensure that communication with CAPCOM is flawless.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:38.20,0:05:43.61,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,But it seems I was a fool to expect him to deliver.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:44.25,0:05:47.34,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,He has nothing in common with me...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.16,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Being on the same wavelength is impossible.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.27,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,Nothing in common?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.41,0:05:56.20,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,You're such a riot...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.20,0:05:57.96,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,What's so funny, Pico?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.44,0:06:03.34,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,Well, I'd say that you have some things in common.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:03.34,0:06:04.40,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,For example...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.17,0:06:10.89,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,You're both members of this huge organization called NASA.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.98,0:06:17.81,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,You should try talking to him.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:18.58,0:06:20.57,Default,Pico,0,0,0,,You might hit it off.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.20,0:06:33.70,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.06,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,What are you so upset about, Nanba?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.58,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.58,0:07:07.19,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,I've been hearing rumors about Hibito.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.40,0:07:12.16,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,How come you call me "Nanba," but you call him "Hibito"?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:12.78,0:07:17.40,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Because Hibito was an astronaut before the rest of us.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.98,0:07:23.75,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Well, I don't really care.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:26.14,0:07:30.84,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,If you happen to see Hibito, tell him to give me a call.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:35.02,0:07:38.31,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Have you had dinner yet, big brother Nanba?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.46,0:07:43.37,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Up for some pizza?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.19,0:08:01.58,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.83,0:08:06.87,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,I met Hibito for the first time here.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.42,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.62,0:08:15.42,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Hey, what was that sound?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.42,0:08:17.09,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,It's very familiar.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.15,0:08:19.77,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Bet you haven't heard it in a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:22.60,0:08:24.82,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,In {\i1}Space Pirate Avant-garde{\i0},
Dialogue: 5,0:08:24.82,0:08:29.07,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,it's the sound effect when the {\i1}Avant-garde{\i0} enters a wormhole.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.57,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.57,0:08:33.70,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's right. I used to watch that anime.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.12,0:08:38.86,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,It's recognizable, so I set it as my ringtone for Hibito's messages.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:38.86,0:08:42.16,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,He was a fan of {\i1}Avant-garde{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.47,0:08:48.29,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Hey, Nanba...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:48.68,0:08:54.26,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Do you remember in survival training, when I told you about my little brother?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.43,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Sure, Kazuya, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.36,0:08:58.86,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Since then,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.94,0:09:02.26,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Kazuya has begun to go outside.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.03,0:09:05.94,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,He's going to school and working part-time.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.57,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Really? That's terrific!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:10.05,0:09:15.48,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,And he's applied to a company in the space industry where he's always wanted to work.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.48,0:09:17.83,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,After passing the written exam, he had an interview.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:17.83,0:09:20.37,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Wow, Kazuya's doing great!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.67,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,One of my college friends works at the company.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:25.74,0:09:29.30,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,He was one of the interviewers, and he had nothing but praise for Kazuya.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.67,0:09:33.53,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,My friend was very positive.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:34.70,0:09:38.36,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,"Nitta Kazuya is a strong candidate who can stand on his own merit.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.36,0:09:40.06,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,He shows promise.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.06,0:09:43.19,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,We should hire him right away."
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.47,0:09:48.96,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,However, it didn't work out...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.98,0:09:50.73,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.02,0:09:55.35,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,My friend was overridden by a number of his superiors.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.91,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,According to them,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:00.69,0:10:03.68,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,someone who's given up and become a shut-in before
Dialogue: 5,0:10:04.50,0:10:05.70,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,may do it again.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:11.90,0:10:15.83,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,If that's the attitude our society wants to take,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.05,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,there isn't much hope.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.49,0:10:20.54,Default,A,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.54,0:10:22.81,Default,A,0,0,0,,Pizza Margherita!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.57,0:10:27.56,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Then, how's Kazuya doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:27.56,0:10:31.61,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,He's been studying conversational English.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:32.98,0:10:36.94,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Next month, he'll be coming here to look for work.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.16,0:10:40.45,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Oh... That's really great.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.81,0:10:46.46,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm sure he'll be fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:46.46,0:10:47.37,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,He can make it.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:48.17,0:10:51.46,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,So I don't need to worry about him.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:51.46,0:10:56.09,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,I'm just a little disappointed by the way the world works.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:05.04,0:11:06.77,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,See ya, Nitta...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.74,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Drive safely.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.74,0:11:09.43,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:14.95,0:11:18.43,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,{\i1}A big brother waiting for his little brother to contact him, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.11,0:11:22.94,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's going through what I did back then...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.35,0:11:40.04,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Looks like...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.85,0:11:42.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I got a message from Hibito.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.46,0:11:45.39,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.92,0:11:46.70,Default,Ni,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:56.02,0:11:58.29,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}"It's been a while, Mu.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.29,0:12:01.50,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was dead for a while,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.50,0:12:03.91,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm coming back to life now.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.37,0:12:11.87,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Right now, I'm wandering around America alone...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:12.89,0:12:15.95,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry for putting you and Apo through this.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.96,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the time being, I won't be coming back to Houston.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.40,0:12:27.43,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've decided to leave NASA."
Dialogue: 5,0:12:28.58,0:12:29.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.24,0:12:41.87,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But you don't have to worry, Mu."
Dialogue: 5,0:12:52.20,0:12:55.03,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,He's that confident, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.04,0:13:07.34,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}He always was able to deliver on his promises.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:08.44,0:13:10.43,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I feel better, Hibito.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.65,0:13:18.26,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I feel better, having learned that you still don't know how to quit.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.24,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Hold on...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:24.24,0:13:29.49,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Does that mean I'm the one in trouble?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.42,signs,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fnPixel Arial 11\xshad-2\yshad-2\b0\an5\fax0.05\blur1.6\c&HAA926E&\frz15.71\fscx225\fscy225\pos(402,272)\4c&H5BB2E4&\4a&H00&\1a&H19&}Okay, Hibito!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.42,signs,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fnPixel Arial 11\shad2\b0\an5\fax0.05\blur1.8\c&H958F7A&\frz15.71\fscx225\fscy225\pos(402,272)\4c&HE28D45&\1a&HFE&\4a&H9C&}Okay, Hibito!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.92,0:13:44.09,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,"From your brother, who is very worried about himself."
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.90,0:13:46.30,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Send.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:48.18,0:13:51.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,If they remove me as CAPCOM...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:51.46,0:13:54.78,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Just stop... Don't think about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:57.02,0:13:57.02,Default,chapter,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 5,0:14:12.26,0:14:17.32,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,JAXA's busy preparing for a few things.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:17.32,0:14:21.35,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,We'll need to meet their conditions.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.05,0:14:24.25,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,This won't be a simple task,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:24.74,0:14:30.93,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,but it's the only way to send Hibito back to the moon.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:32.06,0:14:33.29,Default,But,0,0,0,,Understood...
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.34,0:14:38.74,Default,But,0,0,0,,If this is really what Hibito wants,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:39.68,0:14:43.40,Default,But,0,0,0,,it's his best opportunity.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:45.11,0:14:46.37,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,It isn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:47.16,0:14:51.16,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,He'll just be called a "cosmonaut," rather than an "astronaut."
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.99,Default,Hoshi,0,0,0,,That's what Hibito said...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.92,Default,But,0,0,0,,{\i1}Russia, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.90,0:15:26.11,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,I had my doubts...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.07,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.43,0:15:30.83,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,But after watching you fly,
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.83,0:15:34.61,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,I must ask if you were trained by Deneil Young.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:34.61,0:15:36.54,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Oh, I sure was...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:38.76,0:15:40.38,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Mr. Young trained me.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:40.38,0:15:41.83,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,I'm surprised you could tell.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.32,0:15:46.56,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Then, does everyone Mr. Young trains fly the same way?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:46.56,0:15:52.62,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,No, everyone else Mr. Young trained requested a different instructor before they finished.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:54.21,0:15:56.10,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Uh, Vince...
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.58,0:16:01.56,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:01.95,0:16:05.15,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,This weekend, would you like to go for a drink?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.44,0:16:24.90,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,This is my home.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.40,0:16:28.41,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,I'll introduce you to my family.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.57,Default,Vince,0,0,0,,Come inside.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.74,0:16:32.15,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Thanks for having me!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.22,0:16:40.36,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}The time I spent with Vince and his family gave me a hint as to how I could make it.
