Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.03,0:17:26.16,Default,A,0,0,0,,NETWORK.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:26.16,0:17:27.19,Default,B,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flight is go.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:32.91,0:17:35.60,Default,A,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mars I is go for launch.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:36.52,0:17:38.41,Default,B,0,0,0,,This is it...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.43,0:17:53.84,Default,A,0,0,0,,And what about CAPCOM?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.05,Default,Dami,0,0,0,,We're ready. It's a go.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.57,0:17:57.85,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,Everything's okay here.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:06.22,0:18:07.39,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,It's a go!
