Dialogue: 5,0:19:45.14,0:19:50.58,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}At 8:35 AM, on June 10th, 2028,
Dialogue: 5,0:19:52.21,0:19:55.46,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}while everyone
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.14,0:19:59.79,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}was watching a successful launch...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.07,0:20:08.81,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was remembering the message Hibito had sent me.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:11.85,0:20:14.65,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But you don't have to worry, Mu.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:15.48,0:20:18.44,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't intend to give up on being an astronaut.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.03,0:20:27.87,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I still have a future.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:29.66,0:20:31.83,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Until next time, Mu.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.42,0:20:45.15,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{\i1}See you on the moon."
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.03,0:21:05.75,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}Okay, Hibito...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.67,0:21:09.15,Default,Mu,0,0,0,,{\i1}See you on the moon!
